snippet.title: Wali x Mostafa Atef - Forgive Me (Marhaban Ya Ramadhan) (Official Music Video NAGASWARA)
snippet.description:
Wali x Mostafa Atef - Forgive Me (Marhaban Ya Ramadhan) (Official Music Video NAGASWARA)

Download & Stream: https://lnk.to/ForgiveMeMarhabanYaRamadhan

Menyambut bulan suci Ramadhan, Wali kembali menghadirkan karya religi yang menyentuh hati. Kali ini, Wali berkolaborasi dengan Mostafa Atef, penyanyi religi asal Mesir, dalam single terbaru berjudul â€œForgive Me (Marhaban Ya Ramadhan)â€. Dirilis di bawah label NAGASWARA, lagu ini mengajak pendengar untuk merenungi makna Ramadhan sebagai momen introspeksi diri, rasa syukur, serta memohon ampunan kepada Tuhan.

Diciptakan oleh Apoy, lagu ini hadir dengan lirik yang penuh makna, menggambarkan rasa takut kehilangan kesempatan untuk bertaubat dan menjalani Ramadhan terakhir dalam hidup. Kehadiran Mostafa Atef dalam lagu ini menambah kedalaman spiritual melalui vokal khasnya yang melantunkan bagian-bagian doa dalam bahasa Arab. Kolaborasi ini menjadi perpaduan harmonis antara musik religi Indonesia dengan sentuhan Islami dari Timur Tengah.

Download & Stream: https://lnk.to/ForgiveMeMarhabanYaRamadhan

Menyambut bulan suci Ramadhan, Wali kembali menghadirkan karya religi yang menyentuh hati. Kali ini, Wali berkolaborasi dengan Mostafa Atef, penyanyi religi asal Mesir, dalam single terbaru berjudul â€œForgive Me (Marhaban Ya Ramadhan)â€. Dirilis di bawah label NAGASWARA, lagu ini mengajak pendengar untuk merenungi makna Ramadhan sebagai momen introspeksi diri, rasa syukur, serta memohon ampunan kepada Tuhan.

Diciptakan oleh Apoy, lagu ini hadir dengan lirik yang penuh makna, menggambarkan rasa takut kehilangan kesempatan untuk bertaubat dan menjalani Ramadhan terakhir dalam hidup. Kehadiran Mostafa Atef dalam lagu ini menambah kedalaman spiritual melalui vokal khasnya yang melantunkan bagian-bagian doa dalam bahasa Arab. Kolaborasi ini menjadi perpaduan harmonis antara musik religi Indonesia dengan sentuhan Islami dari Timur Tengah.

snippet.title: A Minecraft Movie | Final Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready for the greatest adventure ever built. â›ï¸ Tickets are on sale NOW for #MinecraftMovie â€“ only in theaters April 4. https://www.fandango.com/MinecraftMovie

From Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures and starring Jason Momoa and Jack Black, â€œA Minecraft Movie,â€ directed by Jared Hess, is the first-ever big screen, live-action adaptation of Minecraft, the best-selling video game of all time. 

The film also stars Emma Myers (â€œWednesdayâ€), Oscar nominee Danielle Brooks (â€œThe Color Purpleâ€), Sebastian Hansen (â€œJust Mercy, â€œLiseyâ€™s Storyâ€), with Jennifer Coolidge. 

Welcome to the world of Minecraft, where creativity doesnâ€™t just help you craft, itâ€™s essential to oneâ€™s survival! Four misfitsâ€”Garrett â€œThe Garbage Manâ€ Garrison (Momoa), Henry (Hansen), Natalie (Myers) and Dawn (Brooks)â€”find themselves struggling with ordinary problems when they are suddenly pulled through a mysterious portal into the Overworld: a bizarre, cubic wonderland that thrives on imagination. To get back home, theyâ€™ll have to master this world (and protect it from evil things like Piglins and Zombies, too) while embarking on a magical quest with an unexpected, expert crafter, Steve (Black). Together, their adventure will challenge all five to be bold and to reconnect with the qualities that make each of them uniquely creativeâ€¦the very skills they need to thrive back in the real world. 

Oscar nominee Hess (â€œNinety-Five Senses,â€ â€œNacho Libreâ€) directed from a screenplay by Chris Bowman & Hubbel Palmer and Neil Widener & Gavin James and Chris Galletta, story by Allison Schroeder and Chris Bowman & Hubbel Palmer, based on the Minecraft video game. Roy Lee, Jon Berg, Mary Parent, Cale Boyter, Jason Momoa, Jill Messick, Torfi Frans Ã“lafsson and Vu Bui produced, and Todd Hallowell, Jay Ashenfelter, Kayleen Walters, Brian Mendoza and Jon Spaihts executive produced. 

The directorâ€™s creative team behind the camera includes BAFTA-nominated director of photography Enrique Chediak (â€œ127 Hours,â€ â€œTransformers: Rise of the Beastsâ€), Oscar-winning production designer Grant Major (â€œThe Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King,â€ â€œThe Megâ€), editor James Thomas (â€œPokÃ©mon: Detective Pikachuâ€, the â€œBoratâ€ films), Oscar-winning VFX supervisor Dan Lemmon (â€œThe Jungle Book,â€ â€œThe Batmanâ€), and costume designer Amanda Neale (â€œThe Meg,â€ â€œWhat We Do in the Shadowsâ€). Casting is by Rachel Tenner. The music supervisors are Gabe Hilfer and Karyn Rachtman, and the music is by Mark Mothersbaugh (â€œThor: Ragnarok,â€ the â€œLEGOÂ®â€ movies). 

Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures Present A Vertigo Entertainment/On The Roam/Mojang Studios Production, A Jared Hess Film, â€œA Minecraft Movie.â€ The film will be distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures worldwide and by Legendary East in China, and released only in theaters and IMAX in North America on April 4, 2025, and internationally beginning 2 April 2025.

snippet.description:

Sporting KC ğŸ†š Inter Miami

#ChampionsCup #concacaf #intermiami #sportingkc #roundone #highlights

 Inter Miami CF earned a 1-nil victory against Sporting Kansas City in the first leg of their Round One Series as the 2025 Concacaf Champions Cup continued Wednesday at Childrenâ€™s Mercy Park in Kansas City, Kansas.

The clearest chances in the first half were courtesy of the visitors, with Luis SuÃ¡rez being just wide of the mark with an attempt from inside the box in the 8â€™ and a long-range right-footed drive in the 38â€™. 

Inter Miami found the opener in the 56â€™ through Lionel Messi, who sent the ball to the back of the net with a right-footed finish inside the box to capitalize on a precise long-ball delivered by Sergio Busquets. 

Messiâ€™s goal against Sporting Kansas City was his first right-footed goal in continental club competition since doing so in the UEFA Champions League with FC Barcelona in 2019 against Manchester United.

Seventeen of Sergio Busquetsâ€™ last 29 assists in all club competitions for FC Barcelona and Inter Miami set up goals scored by Lionel Messi, dating back to March 2016.

Lionel Messi has been involved in 66 goals (52 goals, 14 assists) in 81 career knockout stage matches in continental competitions (UEFA Champions League and Concacaf Champions Cup), including at least one goal involvement in all four of his appearances in the Concacaf Champions Cup (3 goals, 2 assists).

Ã“scar Ustari stood out in goal for the Herons, registering three saves to collect his first clean sheet of the campaign. 

The victory marks the first away win for Inter Miami in the Concacaf Champions Cup.

Erick Thommy attempted seven dribbles against Inter Miami, the most for a Sporting Kansas City player in a Concacaf Champions Cup match since 2016, equaling Yohan Croizetâ€™s against Independiente La Chorrera and Gerso against Monterrey in 2019.

The two clubs will meet again next Tuesday in Florida for their second-leg match. The aggregate winner will advance to the Round of 16.

snippet.title: SOBAT NGARIT PRANK BELI NMAX TURBO 2025
snippet.description:
Pencari Rumput PRANK BELI NMAX TURBO 2025 SEPERTI INI REAKSI MARKETING YAMAHA 


Halo sahabat semua, di video kali ini kami tim Youtube Indonesia Ekspos membuat konten Social Experiment (Prank) Sobat Ngarit beli motor Nmax Turbo 2025 dengan uang cash atau tunai disertai pakaian gembel atau baju gelandang pencari rumput masuk ke Dealer Sepeda Motor Yamaha Panggung Motor di jalan raya Sukowati atau Jl. Maospati - Solo No.161-171, Kebayan 3, Sragen Kulon, Kec. Sragen, Kabupaten Sragen, Jawa Tengah 57212

Tanpa disadari pegawai deler Yamaha Panggung Motor Sragen Sobat ngarit beli motor Yamaha Nmax Turbo dengan membawa karung berisi rumput bercampur uang tunai pada hari Jumat 7 Februari 2025.

Pemilik Video : Khoiri ( Mas Jebleh Youtuber ).
Sales Marketing Yamaha kena prank bernama Putri
Cameraman : Huri Yanto

snippet.title: Jurassic World Rebirth | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
A new era is born. Watch the Jurassic World Rebirth trailer now. 

-----
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@jurassicworld
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/jurassicworld
X: https://twitter.com/jurassicworld
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/jurassicworld
Official Site: https://www.jurassicworld.com/

A new era is born. This summer, three years after the Jurassic World trilogy concluded with each film surpassing $1 billion at the global box office, the enduring Jurassic series evolves in an ingenious new direction with Jurassic World Rebirth. 

Anchored by iconic action superstar Scarlett Johansson, Emmy and SAG nominee Jonathan Bailey and two-time OscarÂ® winner Mahershala Ali, this action-packed new chapter sees an extraction team race to the most dangerous place on Earth, an island research facility for the original Jurassic Park, inhabited by the worst of the worst that were left behind. 

Also starring acclaimed international stars Rupert Friend and Manuel Garcia-Rulfo, the film is directed by dynamic visualist Gareth Edwards (Rogue One: A Star Wars Story) from a script by original Jurassic Park screenwriter David Koepp. 

Five years after the events of Jurassic World Dominion, the planetâ€™s ecology has proven largely inhospitable to dinosaurs. Those remaining exist in isolated equatorial environments with climates resembling the one in which they once thrived. The three most colossal creatures across land, sea and air within that tropical biosphere hold, in their DNA, the key to a drug that will bring miraculous life-saving benefits to humankind.

Academy AwardÂ® nominee Johansson plays skilled covert operations expert Zora Bennett, contracted to lead a skilled team on a top-secret mission to secure the genetic material. When Zoraâ€™s operation intersects with a civilian family whose boating expedition was capsized by marauding aquatic dinos, they all find themselves stranded on a forbidden island that had once housed an undisclosed research facility for Jurassic Park. There, in a terrain populated by dinosaurs of vastly different species, they come face-to-face with a sinister, shocking discovery that has been hidden from the world for decades. 

Ali is Duncan Kincaid, Zoraâ€™s most trusted team member; Critics Choice and Olivier Award winner Jonathan Bailey (Wicked, Bridgerton) plays paleontologist Dr. Henry Loomis; Emmy nominee Rupert Friend (Homeland, Obi-Wan Kenobi) appears as Big Pharma representative Martin Krebs and Manuel Garcia-Rulfo (The Lincoln Lawyer, Murder on the Orient Express) plays Reuben Delgado, the father of the shipwrecked civilian family. 

The cast includes Luna Blaise (Manifest), David Iacono (The Summer I Turned Pretty) and Audrina Miranda (Lopez vs. Lopez) as Reubenâ€™s family. The film also features, as members of Zora and Krebsâ€™ crews, Philippine Velge (Station Eleven), Bechir Sylvain (BMF) and Ed Skrein (Deadpool). 
 
Jurassic World Rebirth is directed by BAFTA winner Edwards from a script by Koepp (War of the Worlds), based on characters created by Michael Crichton. The film is produced by OscarÂ® nominee Frank Marshall and Patrick Crowley, both longtime Jurassic franchise producers and of last summerâ€™s blockbuster, Twisters. The film is executive produced by Steven Spielberg, Denis L. Stewart and Jim Spencer.

snippet.title: Rizwan Fadilah, Nabila Taqiyyah - Tak Satu Cerita (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
#RizwanFadilah #NabilaTaqiyyah #Taksatucerita

Dengarkan Rizwan Fadilah & Nabila Taqiyyah - Tak Satu Cerita

Lagu ini bercerita tentang hubungan penuh makna antara sepasang kekasih yang dulu saling mencintai. Namun, seiring waktu, perbedaan mulai muncul, menciptakan jarak di antara mereka. Percakapan yang dulu penuh pengertian berubah menjadi perdebatan, dan kebiasaan yang dulu indah kini menjadi penghalang. Mereka akhirnya menyadari bahwa tujuan hidup dan impian mereka berbeda, sehingga memutuskan untuk melepaskan satu sama lain demi kebaikan bersama, meski masih saling mencintai.
Sebelum resmi berduet dalam lagu â€œTAK SATU CERITAâ€, Rizwan Fadilah dan Nabila Taqiyyah telah lebih dulu berkolaborasi dengan saling menyanyikan lagu satu sama lain, yang berhasil mendapatkan respons positif dari para penonton. Rizwan dan Nabila pun mengungkapkan rasa bahagia atas terwujudnya duet ini, terutama karena keduanya menyukai lagu tersebut dan merasa vokal mereka berpadu dengan baik. Proses penulisan dan rekaman lagu ini berlangsung menyenangkan dengan banyak diskusi kreatif di antara keduanya. Salah satu momen yang paling berkesan bagi mereka adalah saat pembuatan video musik, di mana mereka saling beradu peran dengan penuh semangat.

localized.description:
#RizwanFadilah #NabilaTaqiyyah #Taksatucerita

Dengarkan Rizwan Fadilah & Nabila Taqiyyah - Tak Satu Cerita

Lagu ini bercerita tentang hubungan penuh makna antara sepasang kekasih yang dulu saling mencintai. Namun, seiring waktu, perbedaan mulai muncul, menciptakan jarak di antara mereka. Percakapan yang dulu penuh pengertian berubah menjadi perdebatan, dan kebiasaan yang dulu indah kini menjadi penghalang. Mereka akhirnya menyadari bahwa tujuan hidup dan impian mereka berbeda, sehingga memutuskan untuk melepaskan satu sama lain demi kebaikan bersama, meski masih saling mencintai.
Sebelum resmi berduet dalam lagu â€œTAK SATU CERITAâ€, Rizwan Fadilah dan Nabila Taqiyyah telah lebih dulu berkolaborasi dengan saling menyanyikan lagu satu sama lain, yang berhasil mendapatkan respons positif dari para penonton. Rizwan dan Nabila pun mengungkapkan rasa bahagia atas terwujudnya duet ini, terutama karena keduanya menyukai lagu tersebut dan merasa vokal mereka berpadu dengan baik. Proses penulisan dan rekaman lagu ini berlangsung menyenangkan dengan banyak diskusi kreatif di antara keduanya. Salah satu momen yang paling berkesan bagi mereka adalah saat pembuatan video musik, di mana mereka saling beradu peran dengan penuh semangat.
